    <p><i>PhD student (secondary supervisor), started Oct 2018.<br />email: <a href="mailto:j.ohagan.1@research.gla.ac.uk">j.ohagan.1@research.gla.ac.uk</a> <br />page: &lt;&gt;</i></p>
    <ul style="overflow: hidden">

  

  

  

  

  

